# Regenerated by `pnpm cf-typegen` (also runs as part of `pnpm typecheck`).
# Committing this caused a real bug: wrangler refuses to overwrite a
# worker-configuration.d.ts it doesn't recognize as its own, so every fresh
# clone's first `pnpm typecheck` failed until the file was deleted by hand.
worker-configuration.d.ts
# The template ships without a lockfile (CI installs with --no-frozen-lockfile);
# a generated store may commit its own by removing this line.
pnpm-lock.yaml
